snippet.title: CAT AND GHOSTLY ROAD - Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Info: https://www.facebook.com/CatAndGhostlyRoad/       
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/994340/Cat_and_Ghostly_Road/    
About: You play as a white cat. Once the painter saved the cat, and they began to live together. But one day a misfortune happened to the man. You need to help the man and save him from death. To do this, you have to go on a dangerous journey to the world of ghosts and demons. Not all things are what they seems: in order to see their true form, you have a special vision.
